OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1779274977
OL,3,C'Sharp' increase in rent prices as
OL,4,Cgovernment reforms come into force `
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FRent prices rose as the government's
OL,8,Fnew rent reforms came into force this
OL,9,Fyear, according to a property website.
OL,11,FFigures show rents increased
OL,12,Fnationwide by 4.4% from December to
OL,13,FMarch this year, the largest quarterly
OL,14,Fincrease recorded by property website
OL,15,FDaft.ie since 2002.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1779274977
OL,3,C'Sharp' increase in rent prices as
OL,4,Cgovernment reforms come into force `
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FMarket rents are now more than one
OL,8,Fthird above their pre-Covid levels and
OL,9,Falmost 80% higher than 10 years ago,
OL,10,Fwhile the availability of rental
OL,11,Faccommodation has increased compared
OL,12,Fwith three months ago and a year ago,
OL,13,Fthe report found.
OL,15,FReport author Professor Ronan Lyons
OL,16,Fsaid the increase in rental
OL,17,Faccommodation should be "interpreted
OL,18,Fwith care".
OL,26,@yD@YOUzD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
