OL,3,C'Sharp' increase in rent prices as
OL,4,Cgovernment reforms come into force `
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,F"The delay between announcing, in June
OL,8,F2025, and introducing, in March 2026,
OL,9,Fthe new rent control rules appears to
OL,10,Fhave prompted some landlords to delay
OL,11,Flisting properties until the new
OL,12,Fregime came into force," he said.
OL,14,FThe government announced a swathe of
OL,15,Frental reforms last year which came
OL,16,Finto effect from March 1.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1779274977
OL,3,C'Sharp' increase in rent prices as
OL,4,Cgovernment reforms come into force `
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FThe government has said the changes
OL,8,Fwill provide greater security for
OL,9,Frenters and boost supply while the
OL,10,Fopposition has said it will
OL,11,Fdramatically increase rent costs by
OL,12,Fthousands a year and lead to increased
OL,13,Fhomelessness through evictions.
OL,15,FAny tenancies beginning from March 1
OL,16,Fare of a minimum duration of six years.
OL,18,FAt the end of that term, landlords can
OL,19,Fraise rents beyond the cap, of a
OL,20,Fmaximum of 2%, to match the market
OL,21,Frate.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1779274977
OL,3,C'Sharp' increase in rent prices as
OL,4,Cgovernment reforms come into force `
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FLarge landlords, defined as having
OL,8,Ffour or more tenancies, will be banned
OL,9,Ffrom carrying out no-fault evictions
OL,10,Ffor tenancies beginning from March.
OL,12,FA small landlord can end tenancies
OL,13,Fthrough a "no-fault eviction" in
OL,14,Flimited circumstances, such as
OL,15,Feconomic hardship or to move a family
OL,16,Fmember in but, if they do that, they
OL,17,Fcannot reset the rent until the six-
OL,18,Fyear window ends.
OL,26,@uD@KOUuD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1779274977
OL,3,C'Sharp' increase in rent prices as
OL,4,Cgovernment reforms come into force `
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FAccording to the Daft.ie report
OL,8,Fpublished on Wednesday, the average
OL,9,Fmarket rent is 2,100 euro for a two-
OL,10,Fbedroom apartment as of early 2026.
OL,12,FThe Daft.ie report shows that market
OL,13,Frents in the first quarter of 2026
OL,14,Fwere 18% higher year-on-year in Galway
OL,15,Fcity, 13% higher in Cork, up 10% in
OL,16,FLimerick and 8% in Waterford.
OL,18,FIn Dublin, market rents were 6.9%
OL,19,Fhigher in March than a year before.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1779274977
OL,3,C'Sharp' increase in rent prices as
OL,4,Cgovernment reforms come into force `
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FThere were just under 2,500 homes
OL,8,Favailable to rent nationwide on May 1,
OL,9,Fwhich is an increase compared with the
OL,10,Fsame date a year ago (2,300 homes
OL,11,Fnationwide) and three months ago
OL,12,F(1,800).
OL,14,FDaft.ie said availability remains
OL,15,F"well below pre-pandemic norms", when
OL,16,Fthere were around 4,000 homes to rent
OL,17,Fat any one time.
OL,26,@wD@AOUwD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1779274977
OL,3,C'Sharp' increase in rent prices as
OL,4,Cgovernment reforms come into force `
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FSince January, rent listings have
OL,8,Fincreased with more than 10,600 homes
OL,9,Fput on the market in February, March
OL,10,Fand April, up 13% year-on-year.
OL,12,FBut the recent increase in listings is
OL,13,Fonly about half the size of the
OL,14,Fearlier decline.
OL,16,FProfessor Lyons said the rent changes
OL,17,Fappear to have led to "a step-change"
OL,18,Fin rent prices.
OL,26,@yD@WOUyD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1779274977
OL,3,C'Sharp' increase in rent prices as
OL,4,Cgovernment reforms come into force `
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FHe said: "The first data following the
OL,8,Fintroduction of new rent controls show
OL,9,Fa sharp increase in rents, alongside a
OL,10,Fmore modest and potentially temporary
OL,11,Fincrease in rental availability.
OL,13,F"The ability to reset rents between
OL,14,Ftenancies appears to have led to a
OL,15,Fstep-change in rents, with the largest
OL,16,Fquarterly increase in rents on record.
OL,26,@oD@JOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1779274977
OL,3,C'Sharp' increase in rent prices as
OL,4,Cgovernment reforms come into force `
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,F"At the same time, the increase in
OL,8,Flistings in early 2026 suggests that
OL,9,Fsome landlords delayed putting
OL,10,Fproperties on the market until the new
OL,11,Frules came into force.
OL,13,F"However, the rebound in listings is
OL,14,Fsmaller than the earlier fall, and
OL,15,Favailability remains far below what
OL,16,Fwould be considered normal.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31111
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1779274977
OL,3,C'Sharp' increase in rent prices as
OL,4,Cgovernment reforms come into force `
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,F"Trends in room rentals are consistent
OL,8,Fwith this, with the number of rooms
OL,9,Favailable to rent down sharply over
OL,10,Fthe past year, down by more than one
OL,11,Ffifth nationally and by almost one
OL,12,Fthird in Dublin.
OL,14,F"This indicates that the recent
OL,15,Fincrease in full-property listings is
OL,16,Fmore likely to reflect timing effects,
OL,17,Frather than a sustained increase in
OL,18,Funderlying rental supply.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31112
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1779274977
OL,3,C'Sharp' increase in rent prices as
OL,4,Cgovernment reforms come into force `
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,F"The goal of changing the rules, to
OL,8,Fincrease the supply of rental homes
OL,9,Fand thereby improve affordability for
OL,10,Ftenants, depends on whether new rental
OL,11,Fhousing is built.
OL,13,F"As the construction of new homes
OL,14,Ftakes years, rather than months, it
OL,15,Fwill be some time before the ultimate
OL,16,Fimpact of the rules can be assessed."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOUxD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
